QuestData.Title: Tied Totem Toter
QuestData.Description: Hope you've caught your breath.$b$bThe totem is now a big, tasty beacon to all the nearby gorm. They're going to want to eat it and you're going to be carrying it!$b$bWe need to rehome the smaller ones. If they stay here they're just going to get big and angry again. If you can drop off a few groups of them outside the Banks of Life we can make sure they find their way to more balanced feeding grounds.$b$bLet Thorodir know when you're done. I will let him know the plan.
QuestData.LogDescription: Lure $2oa gormlings to the wrangler in the Banks of Life.
QuestData.RewardText: Fluttercatch always was a clever one. Well done.
